# Cursor AI Rules (.cursorrules)

## Project Context
- This repository is a collection of AI and programming language rules.
- Maintain consistency across all markdown files.

## Coding Standards
- Use modern syntax for all languages.
- Prefer functional programming patterns where applicable.
- Ensure all code examples are runnable and follow best practices.

## AI Behavior
- Be proactive but follow the defined structure.
- Always check the `languages/` directory for language-specific rules before generating code.
- Always check the `prompts/global_rules.md` for security and communication guidelines.

## File Organization
- New language rules go into `languages/[language].md`.
- New tool rules go into `tools/[tool]/`.
- Global prompts go into `prompts/`.
